1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,000
CMD: "turn around"

2
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,000
CMD: "and go back the opposite direction"

3
00:00:47,370 --> 00:00:52,370
Robot: "I can turn around and then how far should I go back the opposite direction?  You can tell me to move to any object or part of the building you can see, or a distance to move."

4
00:01:01,340 --> 00:01:06,340
CMD: "move to the middle of the building"

5
00:01:32,770 --> 00:01:37,770
Robot: "The middle of the building is outside of my operational zone.  I can move to the middle of this alley, ok?"

6
00:01:34,760 --> 00:01:39,760
CMD: "yes"

7
00:01:53,450 --> 00:01:58,450
Robot: "executing..."

8
00:02:17,450 --> 00:02:22,450
Robot: "done"

